libmicrodns
------------------------------------------
Minimal mDNS resolver (and announcer) library.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.4-1
  libmicrodns-devel-0.2.0-1bl2
  libmicrodns1-0.2.0-1bl2
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.45-1
  cygport-0.37.2-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  meson-1.4.2-1
  ninja-1.13.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/videolabs/libmicrodns

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/videolabs/libmicrodns/archive/refs/tags/0.2.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libmicrodns-0.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libmicrodns-0.2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libmicrodns-0.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmicrodns-0.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmicrodns1-0.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmicrodns-devel-0.2.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libmicrodns)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libmicrodns.README
  /usr/share/doc/libmicrodns/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libmicrodns/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libmicrodns/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/libmicrodns/README.md

(libmicrodns1)
  /usr/bin/cygmicrodns-1.dll

(libmicrodns-devel)
  /usr/include/microdns/microdns.h
  /usr/include/microdns/rr.h
  /usr/lib/libmicrodns.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/microdns.pc

------------------

